%% C4 dynamic — Webhook-triggered event (auth / fail-closed path)
%% Source of truth: docs/adr/ + docs/architecture-brief.md — regenerate via /c4-designer, do not hand-edit
%% Generated: 2026-07-10
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant TRG as External trigger source
    participant SRV as byteswarm Server
    participant BUS as Event Bus

    TRG->>SRV: POST webhook — event + shared secret [webhook/HTTPS]
    SRV->>SRV: validate shared secret (auth port, deny by default)
    alt secret invalid or missing
        SRV-->>TRG: 401 Unauthorized — fail closed, logged [HTTPS]
    else secret valid
        SRV->>BUS: publish event on bw.evt.type.workflowID [NATS]
        BUS-->>SRV: ack — persisted to durable stream [NATS]
        SRV-->>TRG: 202 Accepted [HTTPS]
    end
